Get :- 
                1. get request is to retrieve / fetch information. 
                2. data is used as query string parameter.
                3. data is send as plain text in URL. 
                4. sending data is less secure.



Post :-      
            1. post request is used to create resource.
            2. data is send as request body.
            3. data is send in various formats e.g., json, form data , html, js etc.
            4.  sending data is more secure (not shown in URL).
